channel.title: Would someone please help, i got a question
channel.description: well i downloaded moparscape and have been testing some servers, but im new to this stuff and im just wondering is it safe to go onto Runescape or can they somehow detect iv been playing on a private server? should i delete moparscape first, then start playign runescape again?

item.title: Would someone please help, i got a question
item.dc:creator: @lt_project lt project
item.description:
@lt_project wrote:

moparisthebest:

they cannot detect anything about private servers, they cant detect moparscape, or anything else on your own computer, your safe to play it all you want

ok thank you i think i sent you a pm asking for more help but you can just ignore that
